{
  "texts": [
    "As a result, the impact of AI on the fourth industrial revolution motivates us to focus briefly on \"AI-based modeling\" in this paper.",
    "Artificial intelligence (AI) is a leading technology of the current age of the Fourth Industrial Revolution, with the capability of incorporating human behavior and intelligence into machines or systems [95].",
    "Thus, AI-based modeling is the key to build automated, intelligent, and smart systems according to today's needs.",
    "To solve real-world issues, various types of AI such as analytical, functional, interactive, textual, and visual AI can be applied to enhance the intelligence and capabilities of an application.",
    "However, developing an effective AI model is a challenging task due to the dynamic nature and variation in real-world problems and data."
  ]
}